## Architecture (vue d'ensemble)

- `copier.yml` тАФ questions utilisateur (project_name, scope_profile, tech_profile, commit_language, docs_root, agents, enable_ci_guard) + `_exclude` conditionnel.
- `template/` тАФ racine du template (`_subdirectory: template`, `_templates_suffix: .jinja`).
